# API 接口开发规范

## 核心原则

1. **统一性**: 所有 API 接口遵循相同的设计模式
2. **可预测性**: 响应格式和错误处理保持一致
3. **类型安全**: 使用 TypeScript 定义所有接口类型
4. **错误处理**: 统一的错误处理和用户反馈机制

## 接口定义规范

### 1. 请求响应类型定义

```typescript
// 基础响应类型
interface BaseResponse<T = any> {
	code: number
	message: string
	data: T
	timestamp: number
}

// 分页响应类型
interface PaginatedResponse<T> extends BaseResponse<T[]> {
	pagination: {
		current: number
		pageSize: number
		total: number
		totalPages: number
	}
}

// 错误响应类型
interface ErrorResponse extends BaseResponse<null> {
	error: {
		type: string
		details?: Record<string, any>
		stack?: string // 仅开发环境
	}
}
```

### 2. 请求参数类型定义

```typescript
// 基础分页参数
interface PaginationParams {
	current?: number
	pageSize?: number
}

// 基础查询参数
interface BaseQueryParams extends PaginationParams {
	keyword?: string
	sortBy?: string
	sortOrder?: "asc" | "desc"
}

// 具体业务参数
interface UserQueryParams extends BaseQueryParams {
	status?: "active" | "inactive"
	role?: string[]
	createdAt?: [string, string] // 时间范围
}
```

## API 客户端配置

### 1. 基础配置

```typescript
// apis/clients/base.ts
import axios, { AxiosInstance, AxiosRequestConfig } from "axios"

interface ApiClientConfig {
	baseURL: string
	timeout: number
	retryTimes: number
	retryDelay: number
}

class ApiClient {
	private instance: AxiosInstance
	private config: ApiClientConfig

	constructor(config: ApiClientConfig) {
		this.config = config
		this.instance = axios.create({
			baseURL: config.baseURL,
			timeout: config.timeout,
		})

		this.setupInterceptors()
	}

	private setupInterceptors() {
		// 请求拦截器
		this.instance.interceptors.request.use(
			(config) => {
				// 添加认证头
				const token = localStorage.getItem("token")
				if (token) {
					config.headers.Authorization = `Bearer ${token}`
				}

				// 添加请求ID用于追踪
				config.headers["X-Request-ID"] = generateRequestId()

				return config
			},
			(error) => Promise.reject(error),
		)

		// 响应拦截器
		this.instance.interceptors.response.use(
			(response) => response,
			(error) => this.handleResponseError(error),
		)
	}

	private async handleResponseError(error: any) {
		const { response, config } = error

		// 401 未授权 - 重定向到登录页
		if (response?.status === 401) {
			localStorage.removeItem("token")
			window.location.href = "/login"
			return Promise.reject(error)
		}

		// 403 禁止访问 - 显示权限错误
		if (response?.status === 403) {
			showErrorMessage("您没有权限执行此操作")
			return Promise.reject(error)
		}

		// 网络错误重试
		if (!response && config.retryCount < this.config.retryTimes) {
			config.retryCount = (config.retryCount || 0) + 1
			await delay(this.config.retryDelay)
			return this.instance.request(config)
		}

		return Promise.reject(error)
	}
}
```

### 2. 业务 API 封装

```typescript
// apis/modules/user.ts
import { ApiClient } from "../clients/base"
import type { BaseResponse, PaginatedResponse } from "../types"

interface User {
	id: string
	name: string
	email: string
	avatar?: string
	status: "active" | "inactive"
	createdAt: string
	updatedAt: string
}

interface CreateUserParams {
	name: string
	email: string
	password: string
}

interface UpdateUserParams {
	name?: string
	email?: string
	avatar?: string
}

class UserApi {
	constructor(private client: ApiClient) {}

	// 获取用户列表
	async getUsers(params: UserQueryParams): Promise<PaginatedResponse<User>> {
		const response = await this.client.get("/users", { params })
		return response.data
	}

	// 获取单个用户
	async getUser(id: string): Promise<BaseResponse<User>> {
		const response = await this.client.get(`/users/${id}`)
		return response.data
	}

	// 创建用户
	async createUser(params: CreateUserParams): Promise<BaseResponse<User>> {
		const response = await this.client.post("/users", params)
		return response.data
	}

	// 更新用户
	async updateUser(id: string, params: UpdateUserParams): Promise<BaseResponse<User>> {
		const response = await this.client.patch(`/users/${id}`, params)
		return response.data
	}

	// 删除用户
	async deleteUser(id: string): Promise<BaseResponse<null>> {
		const response = await this.client.delete(`/users/${id}`)
		return response.data
	}
}

export { UserApi, type User, type CreateUserParams, type UpdateUserParams }
```

## 错误处理规范

### 1. 统一错误处理

```typescript
// utils/error-handler.ts
import { message } from "antd"

interface ApiError {
	code: number
	message: string
	type: string
	details?: Record<string, any>
}

class ErrorHandler {
	static handle(error: any): void {
		if (error.response?.data) {
			const apiError: ApiError = error.response.data
			this.handleApiError(apiError)
		} else if (error.code === "NETWORK_ERROR") {
			this.handleNetworkError()
		} else {
			this.handleUnknownError(error)
		}
	}

	private static handleApiError(error: ApiError): void {
		switch (error.type) {
			case "VALIDATION_ERROR":
				this.showValidationError(error.details || {})
				break
			case "BUSINESS_ERROR":
				message.error(error.message)
				break
			case "SYSTEM_ERROR":
				message.error("系统错误，请稍后重试")
				this.reportError(error)
				break
			default:
				message.error(error.message || "请求失败")
		}
	}

	private static handleNetworkError(): void {
		message.error("网络连接失败，请检查网络设置")
	}

	private static handleUnknownError(error: any): void {
		console.error("Unknown error:", error)
		message.error("未知错误，请联系技术支持")
		this.reportError(error)
	}

	private static showValidationError(details: Record<string, any>): void {
		const firstError = Object.values(details)[0]
		if (typeof firstError === "string") {
			message.error(firstError)
		}
	}

	private static reportError(error: any): void {
		// 上报错误到监控系统
		if (process.env.NODE_ENV === "production") {
			// 发送错误报告
		}
	}
}

export { ErrorHandler }
```

### 2. React Hook 封装

```typescript
// hooks/useApi.ts
import { useState, useCallback } from "react"
import { ErrorHandler } from "@/opensource/utils/error-handler"

interface UseApiState<T> {
	data: T | null
	loading: boolean
	error: string | null
}

interface UseApiReturn<T, P extends any[]> extends UseApiState<T> {
	execute: (...params: P) => Promise<T | null>
	reset: () => void
}

function useApi<T, P extends any[]>(apiFunction: (...params: P) => Promise<T>): UseApiReturn<T, P> {
	const [state, setState] = useState<UseApiState<T>>({
		data: null,
		loading: false,
		error: null,
	})

	const execute = useCallback(
		async (...params: P): Promise<T | null> => {
			setState((prev) => ({ ...prev, loading: true, error: null }))

			try {
				const result = await apiFunction(...params)
				setState((prev) => ({ ...prev, data: result, loading: false }))
				return result
			} catch (error) {
				const errorMessage = error instanceof Error ? error.message : "请求失败"
				setState((prev) => ({ ...prev, error: errorMessage, loading: false }))
				ErrorHandler.handle(error)
				return null
			}
		},
		[apiFunction],
	)

	const reset = useCallback(() => {
		setState({ data: null, loading: false, error: null })
	}, [])

	return { ...state, execute, reset }
}

export { useApi }
```

## 使用示例

### 1. 在组件中使用

```tsx
import { useEffect } from "react"
import { useApi } from "@/hooks/useApi"
import { userApi } from "@/opensource/apis"

const UserList = () => {
	const { data: users, loading, execute: fetchUsers } = useApi(userApi.getUsers)

	useEffect(() => {
		fetchUsers({ current: 1, pageSize: 20 })
	}, [fetchUsers])

	if (loading) return <div>Loading...</div>

	return (
		<div>
			{users?.data.map((user) => (
				<div key={user.id}>{user.name}</div>
			))}
		</div>
	)
}
```

### 2. 表单提交

```tsx
import { Form, Input, Button, message } from "antd"
import { useApi } from "@/hooks/useApi"
import { userApi } from "@/opensource/apis"

const CreateUserForm = () => {
	const [form] = Form.useForm()
	const { loading, execute: createUser } = useApi(userApi.createUser)

	const handleSubmit = async (values: any) => {
		const result = await createUser(values)
		if (result) {
			message.success("用户创建成功")
			form.resetFields()
		}
	}

	return (
		<Form form={form} onFinish={handleSubmit}>
			<Form.Item name="name" rules={[{ required: true }]}>
				<Input placeholder="用户名" />
			</Form.Item>
			<Form.Item name="email" rules={[{ required: true, type: "email" }]}>
				<Input placeholder="邮箱" />
			</Form.Item>
			<Form.Item>
				<Button type="primary" htmlType="submit" loading={loading}>
					创建用户
				</Button>
			</Form.Item>
		</Form>
	)
}
```

## 最佳实践

### 1. API 设计原则

- **RESTful**: 遵循 REST 设计原则
- **版本控制**: 使用 URL 版本控制 (`/api/v1/`)
- **状态码**: 正确使用 HTTP 状态码
- **幂等性**: GET、PUT、DELETE 操作保持幂等

### 2. 类型安全

- 所有 API 接口都要有 TypeScript 类型定义
- 使用泛型提高类型复用性
- 请求参数和响应数据都要类型化

### 3. 错误处理

- 统一的错误处理机制
- 用户友好的错误提示
- 开发环境显示详细错误信息
- 生产环境上报错误日志

### 4. 性能优化

- 合理使用请求缓存
- 避免重复请求
- 实现请求取消机制
- 使用防抖和节流

